{"tid":709814,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"噩耗！內馬爾15分鐘訓練都受不了，掩面退場走路都有問題","createTime":"2018-06-20T09:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T13:44:37.000Z","uid":103207,"like":9,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0468d4b9697b737764633689c903f8e16ca031","tid":709814,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:56:36.000Z","msg":"和瑞士的比賽結束後，巴西隊的首次恢復訓練內馬爾就沒有參加，6月19日全隊的第二次訓練，內馬爾出現在訓練場。參加了和瑞士的比賽的球員開始簡單的恢復訓練僅僅15分鐘，內馬爾就相當不舒服，在體能教練的陪伴下走回更衣室。內馬爾走下場的時候還捂著腳踝，似乎腳踝有些問題。<br />\n<br />\n目前巴西足協和教練還沒有對內馬爾的情況進行解釋和說明，他是否在和瑞士的比賽中受傷，或是舊傷復發暫時沒法確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dongtw.com/2018-fifa-world-cup/20180620/857515.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dongtw.com%2F2018-fifa-world-cup%2F20180620%2F857515.html&d=YPzdwoWmyZpliWr0IYlauf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3c75a5f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dongtw.com/2018-fifa-world-cup/20180620/857515.html</a>"},{"pid":"0d3fc1638b9aca68cbae742f846a62b73435934d","tid":709814,"uid":76063,"like":143,"dislike":2,"score":141,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:58:48.000Z","msg":"who is內馬爾"},{"pid":"98616baa43ac6518ab6bd5950e93da11718d0433","tid":709814,"uid":6988,"like":13,"dislike":44,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:59:15.000Z","msg":"內馬爾真是牛B死啦"},{"pid":"589a752f745fef3f6fc22e11e3e682f4708360a1","tid":709814,"uid":886,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T10:00:48.000Z","msg":"下屆再踢囉"},{"pid":"2621a5033572995fe90ad8cdc35e8be91e2cbf41","tid":709814,"uid":22589,"like":8,"dislike":11,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"98616baa43ac6518ab6bd5950e93da11718d0433","tid":709814,"uid":6988,"like":13,"dislike":44,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T09:59:15.000Z","msg":"內馬爾真是牛B死啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T10:01:50.000Z","msg":"卧糟 太牛b了"},{"pid":"99465727975e9924561443ee55af16e6080c6001","tid":709814,"uid":8231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T10:03:23.000Z","msg":"出到都無